Products.RichDescription: Gourmet Garden Lightly Dried Parsley is made with Australian grown organic parsley that is roughly chopped and lightly dried (just enough) for fresher flavour that lasts for 4 weeks once opened. Parsley is best added at the end of your cooking and is ideal in Mediterranean dishes including pasta, dressings, soups and chicken. Refreshes in cooking, unlocking intense flavours. Sprinkle sparingly and season to taste.

Products.RichDescription:
Hand selected at the perfect time, for an optimum, sweeter and traditional tomato flavour.

Source of Vitamin C to support a healthy immune system (1)
(1) As part of a healthy balanced diet.

Veg a day: 1/2 cup = 1 serve of vegetables (2)
(2) One 75g serve contains 13.5g (33% Recommended Dietary Intake) of Vitamin C.

We keep them on the vine, so they continue to ripen and sweeten to a delicious deep red ensuring they are perfect for when you get them home.
To really appreciate this flavour, eat them at room temperature in a basil and mozzarella salad drizzled with olive oil and balsamic vinegar.
